{
  "stem": "15577.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he stole 80% out of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't give it back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so there was a kind of cooperation, because he needed my-- my father more than my father needed him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a year-- I don't remember, exactly, after a year or something, he was sent away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had another one, who was already a German, a real German, because the businesses who-- who were left got-- after a year, the Germans saw that all these people are-- are thieves, and they cannot rely on them.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they changed them for-- for-- but these were already-- only the businesses were left, and they were not too many.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ours was left because, as I told you, it was rather a big one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by the way, we-- we-- have been-- you know Cracow was-- was the capital of the German occupied Poland, because Warsaw was ruined, almost 100%.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Cracow was the capital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the castle of Cracow was reigning the so-called governor, general governor of-- of Poland, who was Mr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Frank.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our-- our-- or my father's business, they all came to my father's business to buy-- so-called-- to buy the fabrics.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were left longer than the others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And maybe because of this, we got, afterwards, German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And your parents and the rest of the employees continued to work there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first time, all of them were working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even I was working there, because after the school was interrupted, everybody had to had-- had to had a job, because then, if you hadn't a job, he was caught, almost every day, to some work, like I told you before, to clean the streets and so on.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was inscribed as a-- a employee in my father's.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
